WEBVTT

00:00:28.320 --> 00:00:31.896
ya bụ na otu ntụpọ mmiri
ma ọ bụ otu mkpụrụ aja

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:33.776
ga eme ya ka ọ mebie.

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:37.056
Ọ na emebikarị, mgbe ọbụla
ana m ebidokarị ya ọtụtụ oge

00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:38.296
tupu ọ rụọ ọrụ

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:41.536
"Biko ọ bụghị ugbua, biko ọ bụghị ugbua," 
e kwuru m n'ime obi m.

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:45.176
Ụgbọ nje m mara jijiji n'aja
m wee jide ume m

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.496
Ọ pere mpe, basaa, na eji oji ka nkume ekpere,

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:50.760
ọ zụrụ obere ụzụ wee
jiri nwayọ bilie n'aja

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:54.256
Ọ mechara, wepụta
ike nke buliri ya

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:55.816
A chịrị m ọchị.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:57.920
Ugbua aga m eru 
n'ugbọelu ahụ n'oge.

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:03.696
e ji m mkpịsịaka hichapụ otjize n'ihu isi m
m wee sekpuru ala